This replication package consists of the following elements:
- Folder "search_selection": contains a .xslx sheet "Search_and_selection" with the following tabs (reflecting the steps in Fig.2 in the paper):
	- Automatic search: containing all search hits (720)
	- Impurity and duplicates removal: list of hits after removal of duplicats and impurities (450)
	- Application of selection criteria: detailed selection form with applied criteria. It results in the list of selected papers (30)
	- Snowballing: list of selected papers after snowballing (34)
- Folder "data_extraction": contains the following items:
	- data_extraction_form: data extraction forms for each of the included primary studies (26) in a plain tab-separated format; this file is used by the R scripts to generate plots and bubble charts
	- input: contains the data extraction forms to input to R scripts
	- output: contains all plots and bubble charts generated through the R scripts
	- R_scripts: contains executable scripts for generation of plots and bubble charts (paths need to be adjusted to the specific location of the main folder)